            <h1 class="gh-article-title">Steal my Code &amp; Save Time: A Step-by-Step Guide to Building a Buttery Smooth, Composable, Health Factor Slider</h1>

                <p class="gh-article-excerpt">Beautiful, robust, design system-worthy slider built with Typescript, React, Radix UI, and Stitches. Perfect for controlling Health Factors and Collateralization Ratios in dApps.</p>

                <figure class="gh-article-image">
        <img
            srcset="../content/images/size/w300/image/fetch/w_2000,h_2000,c_fill,f_jpg,q_auto:good,fl_progressive:steep,g_auto/https-3a-2f-2fsubstack-post-media.s3.amazonaws.com-2fpublic-2fimages-2f6609b3f8-b240-4a44-926e-8fa1210c2fee_1618x938.jpg 300w,
